        Constructor
        Parameters:
        rootIRIString - Ontology root class IRI as string.
        devNumber - The number of device descriptions.
        seed - Random seed for generating randomized device descriptions.
        outputFile - The output ontology as file.
        classConstraintSelectionProbability - The probability of selecting an OWL class constraint (anonymous super class expression) of an OWL named class.
        newIndividualProbability - The probability of creating an OWL named individual.
        classAssertionProbability - The probability of generating class assertion axioms for each named individual.
        objectPropertyAssertionProbability - The probability of creating an object property assertion axiom.
        dataPropertyAssertionProbability - The probability of creating a data property assertion axiom.
        superClassSelectionProbability - The probability of selecting a super class (direct or inferred) of a class for class assertion generation.
        equivalentObjectPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting an equivalent object property (direct or inferred) of an object property for object property assertion generation.
        equivalentDataPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting an equivalent data property (direct or inferred) of a data property for data property assertion generation.
        disjointObjectPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting a disjoint object property of an object property for negative object property assertion generation.
        disjointDataPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting a disjoint data property of a data property for negative object property assertion generation.
        superObjectPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting a super object property (directed or inferred) of an object property for object property assertion generation.
        superDataPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting a super data property (directed or inferred) of a data property for data property assertion generation.
        inverseObjectPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting an inverse property (direct or inferred) of an object property for object property assertion generation.
        symmetricObjectPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting symmetric characteristic of an object property for object property assertion generation.
        asymmetricObjectPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting asymmetric characteristic of an object property for negative object property assertion generation.
        irreflexiveObjectPropertySelectionProbability - The probability of selecting irreflexive characteristic of an object property for negative object property assertion generation.
        manager - Hold of an ontology manager.
        ont - Hold of input ontology.
        extractor - Ontology extractor used for extracting OWL axioms from input ontology.
